data.description: Perched up high with a spectacular view of the San Emigdio Mountains, this is the very first home as you enter the east side of the beautiful Pine Mountain Club community. Magnificent pines adorn the landscape of this quaint cabin, which sits at the very end of Madera Place, with no houses in its views to the east or north. Enjoy the forest mountain views by a cozy wood burning stove with sliding glass doors that open from the living room onto the deck. There is the main bedroom and full bathroom on the first level and on the second level another bedroom and spacious loft. There is also plenty of storage underneath the home. Come enjoy the many amenities of our community & village center, which includes a clubhouse, golf course, 24-hour patrol service, pool, tennis courts, equestrian center, hiking, biking, catch-and-release fishing, grocery store, shops/boutiques and restaurants. And don't forget snow activities on those magical winter days. Come see what mountain living has to offer!
